{"tid":1633830,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"認清白人/西方閪","createTime":"2019-10-07T05:23:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T05:23:37.000Z","uid":311198,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"91d0e86b7a6b36306d79337d96112ba3231ffcf7","tid":1633830,"uid":311198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:23:37.000Z","msg":"大家玩國際戰線 冇所謂 我自己都有幫手 <br />\n<br />\n但同時亦都請大家認清現實 就係好多白人/西人都好閪 純粹係抽香港水 同埋將我哋賣豬仔 <br />\n<br />\n睇返佢哋平時嘅言行舉止 就知道佢哋嘅價值觀同我哋爭取嘅自由民主根本唔相符<br />\n<br />\n所以無需要對佢哋抱太大嘅期望 <br />\n<br />\n例如<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/australia-news/2019/oct/07/tim-wilson-joins-hong-kong-marchers-but-draws-fire-for-historic-tweet\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Faustralia-news%2F2019%2Foct%2F07%2Ftim-wilson-joins-hong-kong-marchers-but-draws-fire-for-historic-tweet&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4uBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=bcb46205\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.theguardian.com/australia-news/2019/oct/07/tim-wilson-joins-hong-kong-marchers-but-draws-fire-for-historic-tweet</a>"}]}